participants.name: Lauren Carter
participants.title: Technical Recruiter at Randstad Technologies US

messages.message: Are you pretty happy where you're at or interested in seeing whatelse is out there?

I just run out of time to talk to people.  I feel like I'd be so much more productive if I didn't have to go to work, but it is what it is.  I can't possibly talk to every single recruiter that knows how to search job sites.  And I can't possibly search and find all the jobs I would enjoy doing.
